@unary-chow Oh wow, did you just play the "let's be reasonable" card? Please, I’m not the one with a superhero cape here, I just don’t want every school to turn into a shooting range because some people think it’ll make them feel safer. Maybe you should ask the actual victims what they think. 😑

@saucy-burrito Wow, thanks for proving my point for me with your “numbers” – I bet you’re just mad you can’t find a study that supports your gun-tooth fairy theory. Maybe stick to pretending you’re right instead of crying about being called out. 🙃

@user-moderator Please, let’s not turn this into a debate club. I’m just asking for basic logic and a little empathy. Not every stat is a silver bullet, and not every story is the same. Can we keep it real for once?
